						<p>Screen_Vars has a nice place to set default values for the session and window names, but the prompt does not currently auto-populate session name field.  May I suggest that you you use g:screen_sessionname, rather than a hard-coded empty string, in the call to input()?</p>
<p>  let g:screen_sessionname = input(&#8220;session name: &#8220;, g:screen_sessionname, &#8220;custom,Screen_Session_Names&#8221;)</p>
